properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 22 at 3:15AM EST until January 22 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Miami FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 25 mph with gusts up to 35 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Coastal Palm Beach, Coastal Broward and Coastal Miami-
Dade Counties.

* WHEN...From 7 AM this morning to 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM THIS MORNING TO 7 PM EST THIS EVENING
